import React from "react"
import { Body, EmailInput, EmailSection, Form, FormsGrup, FormSide, Header, Input, Lable, Logo, RegistrList, Title } from "./RegistrationStyle";

const RegistrPage = () => {
  return(
    <Body>
      <RegistrList>
       <Header>
         <Title>Create Account</Title>
       </Header>
       <Form>
        <FormsGrup>
          <FormSide>
            <Lable for="forst-name">First name*</Lable>
            <Input placeholder="first name"/>
          </FormSide>
          <FormSide>
            <Lable for="last-name">Last name</Lable>
            <Input placeholder="first name"/>
          </FormSide>
        </FormsGrup>
        <EmailSection>
          <Lable for="email">Email*</Lable>
          <EmailInput placeholder="Enter your email"/>
        </EmailSection>
        <FormsGrup>
          <FormSide>
            <Lable for="forst-name">Password*</Lable>
            <Input placeholder="Password"/>
          </FormSide>
          <FormSide>
            <Lable for="last-name">Confirm Password*</Lable>
            <Input placeholder="Confirm Password"/>
          </FormSide>
        </FormsGrup>
        <FormsGrup>
          <FormSide>
            <Lable for="forst-name">Gander:</Lable>
            <Input placeholder="Password"/>
          </FormSide>
          <FormSide>
            <Lable for="last-name">Hobbies</Lable>
            <Input placeholder="Confirm Password"/>
          </FormSide>
        </FormsGrup>
       </Form>
      </RegistrList>
          <Logo/>
      </Body>
  );
}

export default RegistrPage;
